This thesis explores the intersection of micro-quantum technologies and artificial intelligence, specifically focusing on OliviaAI’s use of quantum algorithms to enhance system performance within the TGDK vector. The main objectives of the thesis are as follows:

1. Understanding Micro-Quantum Algorithms: To examine how micro-quantum processes can be applied to enhance AI capabilities and improve system efficiency.


